港最窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地都係用上海話溝通多<br />\n我諗都係身份認同嘅一種啦<br />\n佢地唔鍾意外省人，就好似我地唔鍾意蝗一樣</blockquote><br />\n你呀媽點學識廣東話架<br />\n<br />\n你識唔識講上海話？<br />\n<br />\n你點同你啲表哥表姐溝通？</blockquote><br />\n其實我都覺得我媽好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢初初識我爸嗰陣 佢地係靠寫字溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為老豆係香港人，唔識普通話<br />\n<br />\n後來我媽嫁咗落嚟<br />\n我爸嗰陣成日比廣東歌佢聽<br />\n又成日帶佢去街市買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後慢慢就學識廣東話嗱<br />\n<br />\n上海話我識少少咋<br />\n返上海一般都係用普通話同佢地溝通"},{"pid":"2e687e0c53f5dbb7c225b87d5c35359be795be86","tid":267791,"uid":82562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿媽係上海人<br />\n上海啲姨媽舅父撈得好好<br />\n對比下反而阿媽嫁嚟香港最窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地都係用上海話溝通多<br />\n我諗都係身份認同嘅一種啦<br />\n佢地唔鍾意外省人，就好似我地唔鍾意蝗一樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一鳩樣，親戚個個講緊幾多間樓<br />\n我地就咩都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果而家仲係上海應該有樓有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4f3882767163e2192f9ca43049f9298d67535b","tid":267791,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>阿媽係上海人<br />\n上海啲姨媽舅父撈得好好<br />\n對比下反而阿媽嫁嚟香港最窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地都係用上海話溝通多<br />\n我諗都係身份認同嘅一種啦<br />\n佢地唔鍾意外省人，就好似我地唔鍾意蝗一樣</blockquote><br />\n你呀媽點學識廣東話架<br />\n<br />\n你識唔識講上海話？<br />\n<br />\n你點同你啲表哥表姐溝通？</blockquote><br />\n其實我都覺得我媽好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢初初識我爸嗰陣 佢地係靠寫字溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為老豆係香港人，唔識普通話<br />\n<br />\n後來我媽嫁咗落嚟<br />\n我爸嗰陣成日比廣東歌佢聽<br />\n又成日帶佢去街市買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後慢慢就學識廣東話嗱<br />\n<br />\n上海話我識少少咋<br />\n返上海一般都係用普通話同佢地溝通</blockquote><br />\n你媽係上海人但你唔識上海話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 你媽個陣唔識廣東話都肯嫁落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877e261f9faf355a6773e35f736c5f449bcbccc2","tid":267791,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>阿媽係上海人<br />\n上海啲姨媽舅父撈得好好<br />\n對比下反而阿媽嫁嚟香港最窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地都係用上海話溝通多<br />\n我諗都係身份認同嘅一種啦<br />\n佢地唔鍾意外省人，就好似我地唔鍾意蝗一樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一鳩樣，親戚個個講緊幾多間樓<br />\n我地就咩都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果而家仲係上海應該有樓有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係上海冇祖屋咩？"},{"pid":"1c7e1c13b8b8678869f685bba473441c54a1cfb8","tid":267791,"uid":10587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:11:33.000Z","msg":"上海話識聽唔識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded425781ecd29b5c7143451e6f746bb2133eed2","tid":267791,"uid":56063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上海話識聽唔識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deddd22649ceeb06200effedcc622515cdf5ac98","tid":267791,"uid":9032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:20:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>阿媽係上海人<br />\n上海啲姨媽舅父撈得好好<br />\n對比下反而阿媽嫁嚟香港最窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地都係用上海話溝通多<br />\n我諗都係身份認同嘅一種啦<br />\n佢